{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"AuDqSlWn0PlsSo8JdLgrR","title":"Software","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"type":"note","desc":"","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"Software","id":"AuDqSlWn0PlsSo8JdLgrR","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"Software.AWS","alias":"Software.AWS","position":{"start":{"line":30,"column":5,"offset":738},"end":{"line":30,"column":21,"offset":754},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"Software.AWS"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"Software","id":"AuDqSlWn0PlsSo8JdLgrR","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"Software.HPC","alias":"Software.HPC","position":{"start":{"line":34,"column":5,"offset":776},"end":{"line":34,"column":21,"offset":792},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"Software.HPC"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"Software","id":"AuDqSlWn0PlsSo8JdLgrR","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"Software.Git","alias":"Software.Git","position":{"start":{"line":38,"column":5,"offset":806},"end":{"line":38,"column":21,"offset":822},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"Software.Git"}}],"anchors":{"r":{"type":"header","text":"R","value":"r","line":10,"column":0},"citrix":{"type":"header","text":"Citrix","value":"citrix","line":20,"column":0},"eviews":{"type":"header","text":"EViews","value":"eviews","line":28,"column":0},"aws":{"type":"header","text":"AWS","value":"aws","line":34,"column":0},"monarchhpc":{"type":"header","text":"MONARCH/HPC","value":"monarchhpc","line":38,"column":0},"git":{"type":"header","text":"Git","value":"git","line":42,"column":0}},"fname":"Software","updated":1636428260839,"created":1636427887650,"parent":"PhD","children":["pHk638EFKNsd7l8ofo19m","DnfP7up0cIhvaUWp23Jtk","Pn4jty9CxKSvbfTSqLMj3","3aMMcBxQ33Km5ovBrmbT6"],"data":{},"contentHash":"29b8cb07378cdf30e90ae370747cb2ae","custom":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"software\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#software\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Software</h1>\n<p>Some documentation for quick fixes regarding software.</p>\n<h2 id=\"r\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#r\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>R</h2>\n<p>Compilation (and installation) of some packages requires the avialability of C++ compilers.</p>\n<p>Windows - Rtools</p>\n<p>MacOS - Xcode build tools</p>\n<p>Linux - gcc</p>\n<h2 id=\"citrix\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#citrix\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Citrix</h2>\n<p>In most of the occasions we might need set a link to Firefox's keystore to Citrix &#x26; below command will help to set the link to Firefox's keystore to Citrix</p>\n<pre><code>sudo ln -s /usr/share/ca-certificates/mozilla/* /opt/Citrix/ICAClient/keystore/cacerts\n</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"eviews\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#eviews\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>EViews</h2>\n<p>Citrix tries to mount local drives as \"network\" drives in the remote session. If this does not work, try adjusting the permissions setting in the relevant Citrix app.</p>\n<p>Linking with Google Drive is possible, but reportedly very finicky.</p>\n<h2 id=\"aws\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#aws\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>AWS</h2>\n<p>See <a href=\"/notes/pHk638EFKNsd7l8ofo19m\">Amazon Web Services</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"monarchhpc\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#monarchhpc\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>MONARCH/HPC</h2>\n<p>See <a href=\"/notes/Pn4jty9CxKSvbfTSqLMj3\">HPC</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"git\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#git\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Git</h2>\n<p>See <a href=\"/notes/DnfP7up0cIhvaUWp23Jtk\">Gir Workshop and Notes</a></p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"children\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#children\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Children</h2>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"/notes/pHk638EFKNsd7l8ofo19m\">Amazon Web Services</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/notes/DnfP7up0cIhvaUWp23Jtk\">Gir Workshop and Notes</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/notes/Pn4jty9CxKSvbfTSqLMj3\">HPC</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/notes/3aMMcBxQ33Km5ovBrmbT6\">Tensorflow</a></li>\n</ol>","noteIndex":{"id":"PhD","title":"PhD Homepage","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"type":"note","desc":"","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"PhD","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"roadmap","alias":"roadmap","position":{"start":{"line":12,"column":1,"offset":451},"end":{"line":12,"column":12,"offset":462},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"roadmap"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"PhD","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"Meeting","alias":"Meeting","position":{"start":{"line":14,"column":1,"offset":464},"end":{"line":14,"column":12,"offset":475},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"Meeting"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"PhD","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"TODO","alias":"TODO","position":{"start":{"line":16,"column":1,"offset":477},"end":{"line":16,"column":9,"offset":485},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"TODO"}}],"anchors":{"quick-links":{"type":"header","text":"Quick Links","value":"quick-links","line":17,"column":0}},"fname":"root","updated":1637563604861,"created":1595961348801,"parent":null,"children":["t58wEmhAtf1GlHmO","Wnsnl9Ff8hLGapBoL37BK","CQTUwoXQNcd0Y7la7IaAn","9s2d4L1UHWFWCdtORYT2Q","AiXOWFsdvi3BPZxcUMjIi","MsmFdXyWfizd5g8GGcObD","MXHvc8bQbNRRVCB0UogRy","T4FN6sDHfA9wxiZ7Dg5WX","jtZSk246bVVDfJy6cdpS1","2qGHFR7CcKOE0Meu7UU6D","qGmGYptDK